FBIS4-5406 "dreas069_a_94010" FBIS-EAS-94-069 Daily Report 9 Apr 1994 NORTHEAST ASIA Japan Debate on Successor to Hosokawa Continues Debate on Successor to Hosokawa Continues Official: Hosokawa Supports Hata OW0904134794 Tokyo KYODO in English 1341 GMT 9 Apr 94 OW0904134794 Tokyo KYODO English BFN [Text] Tokyo, April 9 KYODO -- Prime Minister Morihiro Hosokawa wants Foreign Minister Tsutomu Hata to be his successor, a senior coalition official said Saturday.
